 class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-908\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-To-768x442-2.png\" alt=\"estimate to bill\" width=\"768\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-To-768x442-2.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-To-768x442-2-300x173.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-To-768x442-2-60x35.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-To-768x442-2-150x86.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Billing and Shipping &#8211;\u00a0<\/strong>If you\u00a0change the billing and shipping informations after slecting a client and click on the edit icon, this will be changed for the Estimate but in the\u00a0customer profile the informations will remain the same and wont be any changes in the Invoice.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-909\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-to-Edit-768x442-3.png\" alt=\"estimate bill to edit\" width=\"768\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-to-Edit-768x442-3.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-to-Edit-768x442-3-300x173.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-to-Edit-768x442-3-60x35.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Bill-to-Edit-768x442-3-150x86.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Number\u00a0<\/strong>&#8211; Number is automatically populated Eq. 001 next will be 002.<\/p>\n<p>This number its fetched from <strong>Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;Finance-&gt;Estimates<\/strong>\u00a0 &#8211; Next\u00a0<strong>\u00a0<\/strong>Number the number its auto increment but you can change the next number in\u00a0<strong>Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;Finance-&gt;Estimates.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-910\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Next-Number-768x319-4.png\" alt=\"estimate next number\" width=\"768\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Next-Number-768x319-4.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Next-Number-768x319-4-300x125.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Next-Number-768x319-4-60x25.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Next-Number-768x319-4-150x62.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Status &#8211; <\/strong>By default the draft status will be selected, you can change the status anytime you want, note that when you send the estimate to your customer the status will be change auto to SENT.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Currency<\/strong>\u00a0&#8211; The currency is automatically selected based on your default currency or currency set for the selected Customer you\u00a0selected previously in the customer profile. If the currency for this customer is <strong>USD<\/strong> it will be automaticly selected and cannot be changed, read more <a href=\"https:\/\/www.perfexcrm.com\/faqs\/how-to-record-transaction-in-other-currency-then-the-base-currency\/\">here<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Sale Agent<\/strong> &#8211; You can select sale agent for this estimate then then generate reports in <strong>Reports-&gt;Sales-&gt;Estimate Report<\/strong>. Note that the sale agent full name will be shown on the estimate if in<strong> Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;Finance-&gt;Estimates<\/strong> -&gt; Show sale agent on estimate is set to yes.<\/p>\n<p>You can add<strong> Estimate items<\/strong>, when adding make sure u click on the blue check icon in order the item to be added you can also select tax options see shown in picture.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-911\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Add-New-Item-768x374-5.png\" alt=\"estimate add new item\" width=\"768\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Add-New-Item-768x374-5.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Add-New-Item-768x374-5-300x146.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Add-New-Item-768x374-5-60x29.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Add-New-Item-768x374-5-150x73.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The items will be stored separately for each estimate and changing the items informations in Sales-&gt;Items wont affect the already created estimates with specific item\/s.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Admin<\/strong> note is only for admins\/staff members.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Customer note<\/strong> is visible to client side also, on the HTML estimate and PDF estimate.<\/p>\n<p>You can setup terms directly in the estimate or you can have predefined terms which will be auto populated. <strong>To setup <\/strong><span id=\"predefined_terms\"><strong>predefined terms and conditions navigate\u00a0to<\/strong> <strong>Setup -&gt; Settings -&gt; Finance -&gt; Estimate\u00a0<\/strong>scroll down and you can populate the fields as it fits you.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-912\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Predefined-Notes-768x223-6.png\" alt=\"estimate predefined notes\" width=\"768\" height=\"223\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Predefined-Notes-768x223-6.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Predefined-Notes-768x223-6-300x87.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Predefined-Notes-768x223-6-60x17.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Estimate-Predefined-Notes-768x223-6-150x44.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Click\u00a0submit<\/strong> to save the estimate.<\/p>\n<p>While editing\/creating estimate\u00a0the <b>adjustment option<\/b> is always available if you want to +- the total amount<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>To create new estimate\u00a0go to Sales -&gt; Estimates -&gt; Create New\u00a0Estimate or by clicking on the Build icon on the top left side and click Create Estimate Client &#8211; Before selecting a client you must have added clients Customers-&gt;New Customer. When selecting a Customer the customer informations will be fetched directly from the customer profile [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[18,16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-906","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-estimates","category-sales"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/906","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=906"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/906\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[